<h1>It's like you don't care.</h1>

<p>Hello there <%= @user.first_name %></p>

<p>Seeing as you are a forgetful person this might be hard for you,
   but we'll try it anyway.</p>

<p>Click the link below.  Follow instructions.</p>

<p><%= link_to "You can do it. Click me.",
    edit_password_reset_url(@user.reset_token, email: @user.email) %></p>

<p>Go for it...or just in case, the link will expire in 2 hours.</p>

<p>If you did not request this email, you're in more trouble than we thought,
   but the good news is your March Madness password isn't going to change. </p>
